author: ddas
msg: MAPREDUCE-1383. Automates fetching of delegation tokens in File*Formats Distributed Cache and Distcp. Also, provides a config  mapreduce.job.hdfs-servers that the jobs can populate with a comma separated list of namenodes. The job client automatically fetches delegation tokens from those namenodes. Contributed by Boris Shkolnik.
